Tool of the Day: Gemini AI – brainstorm content ideas.

Theory 
AI generates many ideas quickly, avoiding blank-page stress.
It connects different fields (food + fashion, tech + art) for fresh ideas.
You can refine outputs by asking AI to simplify, expand, or change style.
AI personalizes ideas to your tone, audience, and goals.
Helps in prototyping — drafts, captions, scripts, even basic code..
